OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F427A1772565069
OL,3,CWoman dies in crash after car fleeing
OL,4,Cpolice drives on wrong side of road
OL,6,FA woman has died in a crash after a
OL,7,Fcar fleeing the police drove on the
OL,8,Fwrong side of a dual carriageway,
OL,9,Fpolice said.
OL,11,FThe fatal collision took place in
OL,12,FSunderland at around 3am on Sunday (1
OL,13,FMarch) and involved a grey Volkswagen
OL,14,FSharan and a white BMW, Northumbria
OL,15,FPolice said.
OL,17,FA 24-year-old man ` the driver of the
OL,18,FBMW ` was arrested on suspicion of
OL,19,Fcausing death by dangerous driving and
OL,20,Fremains in police custody at this
OL,21,Ftime, the force added.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/8
