PN,42702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F427A1772565069
OL,3,CWoman dies in crash after car fleeing
OL,4,Cpolice drives on wrong side of road
OL,6,FOfficers on duty had spotted the white
OL,7,FBMW at around 2.55am as it travelled
OL,8,Fon the A184 in the Felling area of
OL,9,FGateshead.
OL,11,FA pursuit began after the vehicle
OL,12,Ffailed to stop when instructed by
OL,13,Fpolice.
OL,15,FThe same vehicle was sighted
OL,16,Ftravelling south on the northbound
OL,17,Fcarriageway of the A19 in Sunderland
OL,18,Fminutes before the crash, police said.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
