OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,428,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F427A1772565069
OL,3,CWoman dies in crash after car fleeing
OL,4,Cpolice drives on wrong side of road
OL,6,F"Emergency services attended where
OL,7,Fsadly a female passenger from the BMW
OL,8,Fwas confirmed deceased at the scene,"
OL,9,Fa spokesperson for Northumbria Police
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,F"The family of the woman ` aged in her
OL,13,F20s ` have been informed and are being
OL,14,Foffered support by specially trained
OL,15,Fofficers."
OL,17,FA male passenger ` also in his 20s `
OL,18,Fsustained serious injuries and was
OL,19,Ftaken to hospital where he remains in
OL,20,Fa life-threatening condition, the
OL,21,Fforce said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@eO]tD@AOUwD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,428,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F427A1772565069
OL,3,CWoman dies in crash after car fleeing
OL,4,Cpolice drives on wrong side of road
OL,6,FThe male driver of the Sharan was also
OL,7,Ftaken to hospital for treatment, but
OL,8,Fhis injuries are not deemed to be
OL,9,Fserious.
OL,11,FThe A19 was closed in both directions
OL,12,Fbetween the junctions of the A1231 at
OL,13,FHylton Grange and the A184 Testos
OL,14,Froundabout for several hours after the
OL,15,Fcrash.
OL,17,FIt has since re-opened to traffic,
OL,18,FNorthumbria Police said.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,428,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F427A1772565069
OL,3,CWoman dies in crash after car fleeing
OL,4,Cpolice drives on wrong side of road
OL,6,FThe force also said it has referred
OL,7,Fthe case to the Independent Office for
OL,8,FPolice Conduct (IOPC) for
OL,9,Finvestigation.
OL,11,F"Firstly, our thoughts go out to the
OL,12,Fwoman's loved ones as they process
OL,13,Fthis tragic news, and also to the
OL,14,Ffamilies of those injured," Sergeant
OL,15,FGreg Huntley, of Northumbria Police's
OL,16,FSerious Collision Investigation Unit,
OL,17,Fsaid.
OL,26,@sD@AOUvD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,428,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F427A1772565069
OL,3,CWoman dies in crash after car fleeing
OL,4,Cpolice drives on wrong side of road
OL,6,F"A section of the A19 was closed as
OL,7,Four officers and the IOPC carried out
OL,8,Fenquiries at the scene, but the road
OL,9,Fhas since been re-opened to traffic.
OL,11,F"We'd like to thank the public for
OL,12,Ftheir patience today while this was
OL,13,Fongoing and would ask people to please
OL,14,Frefrain from any speculation online
OL,15,Fand in the community in the meantime."
OL,17,FAn IOPC spokesperson said: "Our
OL,18,Finvestigation will look at police
OL,19,Factions prior to the fatal collision.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUwD@fO]yD@\OU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,428,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F427A1772565069
OL,3,CWoman dies in crash after car fleeing
OL,4,Cpolice drives on wrong side of road
OL,6,F"After being notified by the force, we
OL,7,Fsent investigators to attend the scene
OL,8,Fand the police post incident
OL,9,Fprocedures to begin gathering evidence
OL,10,Fand declared an independent
OL,11,Finvestigation earlier today.
OL,13,F"We will be contacting the woman's
OL,14,Ffamily to offer our condolences and
OL,15,Fexplain our role.
OL,17,F"Our thoughts are with everyone
OL,18,Faffected by this incident."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUyD@AOUzD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/8
